          </h2>
          <p class=3D"text-base dark:text-[#F8F8F8]">
            A truth table is a simple chart that shows how a logic statemen=
t works. It lists all the possible outcomes
            of a logical expression or circuit based on its inputs. Truth t=
ables use binary values, where each input can
            be either 1 (true) or 0 (false).
            <br>
